                        <foliation xml:id="original">
                           <p>Foliated on folios <locus from="1b" to="233">1b to 233b</locus> in Hindu-Arabic numerals inscribed on the upper-right corners of the b sides in black <material>ink</material>.</p>
                        </foliation>
                        <foliation xml:id="modern">
                           <p>Later European foliation in pencilled Arabic on the upper-right corners of the b sides from folios <locus from="134Ab" to="205Aa">134Ab to 205Aa</locus>, bcommence with 134 instead of 234, hence thereafter off by 100; however, they are followed for this record.</p>
                        </foliation>
                        <collation>
